column1: "Is there any problem if i am located in chittagong??"

"I wanted to do a collaboration. I found that you use so many wooden items like wall floating shelves, hanging lamps etc. I do have a business making those. I can deliver your customer all those items at a reasonable price, additional to that I am willing to share a portion of my profit with you per order."
"Can you tell me more about your ad?"
"Can you tell me more about your ad?"
"We are committed to deliver quality. We offer 7 days money back gurrenty as well as 5 years warrenty. I think we really could work together.\nKindly share your thoughts"
"I loved your work in this video"
"Design Pete kotodin shomoy lagte pare approximately? Amar onk Tara ache."
"master bed ta cancel koran only dinning room"
"But my room size is very small"
"Can you send me some simple ideas"

"Add me on Meet so we can video chat. Use this link: https://duo.app.goo.gl/4HymGci"
